Rating: 4
Made a vegetarian version of this and it was great! I substituted Field Roast sausage for the Chorizo (and cooked it separately to keep the texture), adding just one to the early stage for added flavor and used a vegetarian broth. I also added garlic tops (with the peas), onions and garlic (at the start) for added flavor. Loved it, will definitely make again.

