This was incredible. Hunt down smoked paprika (we used hot) - it really made the dish!

Rating: 4
This recipe is delicious. Of course, a few changes-just 2 of us, so we used 3 small split lobster tails and 6 shrimp. Cut the recipe in half, and couldn't find short grained rice (even Whole Foods didn't have any). Substituted a long grain. Used leeks, and added 2 minced garlic cloves. Can't wait to make this for our grown kids.

Rating: 4
Subbed a seafood medley, shrimp, scallops, mussels, & calimari for the lobster. Good stuff. Will fine tune, until get the crusty bottom.